#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Today's topic is about spending one-on-one time with our teens. \n"
"\n"
"Being a parent can be so hard. Sometimes it feels like our teens never listen to us.\n"
"\n"
"But science shows that spending just a few minutes each day of focused one-on-one time with your teen helps build trust and love."
msgstr ""
"Isihloko sanamhlanje simalunga nokuchitha ixesha lomnye nomnye kunye nabantwana bethu abafikisayo. \n"
"\n"
"Ukuba ngumzali kunganzima. Ngamanye amaxesha kuvakala ngathi abantwana bethu abasimameli.\n"
"\n"
"Kodwa ingcali zisibonisa ukuchitha imizuzwana embalwa ngosuku nigxile kwixesha lomnye nomnye kunye nomntwana wakho ofikisayo kungancedisa ukwakha ukuthembana kunye no thando."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Why is spending one-on-one time with your teens important? Tap play to learn"
msgstr "Kutheni kubalulekile ukuchitha ixesha lomnye nomnye kunye nabantwana bethu abafikisayo? Cofa udlala ukuze ufunde"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Hello.\n"
"\n"
"Our topic today is one-on-one time with our children.\n"
"\n"
"It is important to spend time with our children so that they can get to understand us, and for us to get an opportunity to understand them.\n"
"\n"
"Remember, a family with good understanding lives in harmony."
msgstr ""
"Molo. \n"
"\n"
"Isihloko sanamhlanje singokuchitha ixesha kunye nabantwana bethu sisodwa. \n"
"\n"
"Kubalulekile ukuchitha ixesha kunye nabantwana bethu ukuze basazi, ukwenzela nathi sifumane ithuba lokuba sibazi.\n"
"\n"
"Khumbula, usapho olwazanayo luphila ngoxolo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Let's discuss, what is one-on-one time?\n"
"\n"
"One-on-one time is when you focus on your teens, without distractions like TVs or phones. Let your teens take the lead in choosing what you do or talk about.\n"
"\n"
"It is great if you can spend fifteen minutes a day together, but even five minutes a day is really good."
msgstr ""
"Makhe sixoxe, yintoni ixesha lomnye nomnye?\n"
"\n"
"Ixesha lomnye nomnye kuxa unike ingqwalasela kubantwana bakho abafikisayo, ngaphandle kweziphazamisi ezinje ngo MABONAKUDE okanye ifowuni. Yeka abantwana bakho abafikisayo bakhokhele ekukhetheni into eninokuyenza okanye eninokuthetha ngayo.\n"
"\n"
"Kungakuhle ukuchitha imizuzu elishumi elinesihlanu ngosuku kunye, kodwa nemizuzu emihlanu ngosuku nayo ilungile."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_female_1.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Hear how one-on-one time helped @data.characters.media_female_1.name and her teen"
msgstr "Mamela limnceda njani ixesha lomnye nomnye @data.characters.media_female_1.name kunye nomntwana wakhe"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"When I first heard I had to spend One-on-One Time with my teen, it was hard for me. I did not know when to do it or what to say. I did not want to spoil my teen so that he thinks we have to do everything together.\n"
"\n"
"But I really wanted to build my relationship with my teen and I wanted him to open up about what was troubling him. So we tried the One-on-One Time.\n"
"\n"
"First, it felt weird, but it turned out to be fun! Now we watch his TV programme together and we chat about it. And we can even talk about how my son is changing into adolescence and even about girlfriends and those things!"
msgstr ""
"Xana ndandiqala ukuva ukuba kufuneka ndichithe Ixesha Lomnye Nomnye kunye nomntwana wam ofikisayo, kwakunzima kum. Ndandingayazi ukuba mandiyenze nini okanye yintoni emandiyithethe. Ndandingafuni ukumosha umntwana wam ofikisayo ukwenzela acinge kufuneka senze yonke into kunye.\n"
"\n"
"Kodwa ndandifuna nyhani ukwakha ubudlelwane nomntwana wam ofikisayo kwaye ndandifuna avule isifuba malunga nento emhluphayo. Ngoko sazama Ixesha Lomnye Nomnye kunye.\n"
"\n"
"Ekuqaleni ibivakala ingaqhelekanga, kodwa iphele isonwabisa! Ngoku sibukela inkqubo yakhe kwi TV kunye kwaye sincokole ngayo. kwaye siyathetha nkqu malunga nohlobo unyana wam atshintsha ngalo ekubeni engumntana ofikisayo, kunye nangamantombazane nezinye izinto!"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f3_uncle.name
#.      @data.characters.f3_daughter_12.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Teens enjoy one-on-one time in different ways. What matters most is following your teen’s lead and letting them choose how to spend the time together. \n"
"Let’s see how @data.characters.f3_uncle.name and @data.characters.f3_daughter_12.name do this together."
msgstr ""
"Abantwana abafikisayo bayalithanda ixesha lomnye nomnye ngeendlela ezahlukeneyo. Okona kubaluleke ngamandla kukulandela isikhokelo somntwana wakho ofikisayo kwaye umvumele ibenguye okhetha ukuba nilichitha njani ixesha kunye. \n"
"Makhe sibone benza njani u@data.characters.f3_uncle.name no @data.characters.f3_daughter_12.name lento kunye."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f3_daughter_12.name! should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Hi @data.characters.f3_daughter_12.name! I have 5 minutes of one-on-one time before I leave for work. What would you like to do together?"
msgstr "Molo @data.characters.f3_daughter_12.name! Ndinemizuzu emi- 5 yexesha lethu sobabini phambi kokuba ndihambe ndiye emsebenzini. Yintoni obungathanda siyenze kunye?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I was about to do my Geography project. We have to find the capital cities of all the East African countries. Can you help me with that?"
msgstr "Bendisezokuqala ukwenza iprojekthi yam ye Geography. Kufuneka sifumane idolophu ezinkulu kuwo onke amazwe ase Mpuma Africa. Ungandinceda ngalonto?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Of course! How can I help?"
msgstr "Ngokuqinisekileyo! Ndingakunceda njani?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Great! I can remember the countries, and you could write them down? Then we can look up the capitals on your phone."
msgstr "Kulungile! Ndingawakhumbula amazwe, kwaye ungawabhala phantsi? Emva koko sijonge ikomkhulu e fowunini yakho."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Very good. Let’s do that."
msgstr "Kuhle kakhulu. Masenze lonto."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "_5 minutes later..._"
msgstr "_emva kwemizuzu emi 5..._"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Wow, you remembered all the countries! And you were so clever to find the capital cities using the phone."
msgstr "Kwakuhle. Uwakhumbula onke amazwe! Kwaye uye wahlakanipha kakhulu ukufumana amazwe neekomkhulu ngokusebenzisa ifowuni."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Thank you, uncle. Can I go on TikTok now?"
msgstr "Enkosi, malume. Ndingaya kuTikTok ngoku?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"You can have 30 minutes on TikTok after you finish your homework. \n"
"I would also love to try TikTok. Can you help me set up an account tomorrow?"
msgstr ""
"Ungayifumana i mizuzu eyi 30 kuTikTok emva kokuba ugqibe umsebenzi wakho wasekhaya.\n"
"Ndingathanda nam ukuzama uTikTok. Ungandinceda ukwenza i akhawunti kuTikTok ngomso?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes, of course! Then I can show you that cool video I told you about yesterday."
msgstr "Ewe, nakanjani! emva koko ndingakubonisa la video intle bendikuxelela ngayo izolo."

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f3_uncle.name
#.      @data.characters.f3_daughter_12.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"@data.characters.f3_uncle.name and @data.characters.f3_daughter_12.name showed us how one-on-one time can be simple and fun. They listened to each other, shared tasks, and laughed together.\n"
"Now, let’s think about what made this time successful for them — and why it matters that all caregivers spend time with their teens."
msgstr ""
"U @data.characters.f3_uncle.name kunye no @data.characters.f3_daughter_12.name basibonisile ukuba ixesha lomnye nomnye lingalula kwaye lonwabise. Bayamamelana omnye nomnye, babelana ngemisebenzi, kwaye bahleka kunye.\n"
"Ngoku, makhe sicinge malunga nokuba yintoni eyenze elixesha liphumelele kubo - kwaye kutheni kubalulekile ukuba bonke abakhathaleli bachitha kunye ixesha nabantwana babo abafikisayo."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f3_uncle.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What does @data.characters.f3_uncle.name do to make one-on-one time successful?"
msgstr "Ingaba wenza ntoni u@data.characters.f3_uncle.name ukwenza ixesha lomnye nomnye libeyimpumelelo?"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f3_daughter_12.name’s should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Listen and follow @data.characters.f3_daughter_12.name’s lead"
msgstr "Mamela kwaye ulandele isikhokelo sika@data.characters.f3_daughter_12.name"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f3_daughter_12.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Praise @data.characters.f3_daughter_12.name"
msgstr "Ncoma u@data.characters.f3_daughter_12.name"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f3_daughter_12.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Focus on @data.characters.f3_daughter_12.name (no distractions)"
msgstr "Gxila ku@data.characters.f3_daughter_12.name (kungabikho ziphazamiso)"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Set a clear time limit"
msgstr "Misela ixesha elicacileyo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Make it fun"
msgstr "Yenze yonwabise"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f3_uncle.name
#.      @data.characters.f3_daughter_12.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f3_uncle.name shows that even a short time together can be special. He listens, gives praise, and keeps the moment enjoyable. This helps @data.characters.f3_daughter_12.name feel supported and proud."
msgstr "U@data.characters.f3_uncle.name ubonisile ukuba nexesha elincinci kunye lingaba lelikhethekileyo. Uyamamela, ancome kwaye agcine ixesha lisonwabisa. Lento inceda u@data.characters.f3_daughter_12.name azive exhaswa kwaye enebhongo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "True or False? All caregivers need to spend one-on-one time with their teens."
msgstr "Yinyani okanye asiyonyani? Bonke abanakekeli badinga ukuchitha ixesha lomnye nomnye kunye nabantwana babo abafikisayo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "True"
msgstr "Yinyani"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That’s right! Teens feel more loved and supported when each caregiver spends time with them in their own way. Caring role models can help teens feel more confident, do better in school, and avoid risky behaviour."
msgstr "Kulungile! Abantwana abafikisayo baziva bethandwa kwaye bexhaswa xana umnakekeli ngamnye echitha ixesha nabo ngendlela abafuna ngayo. Imizekelo yabantu abanenkathalo inokunceda abantwana abafikisayo bazive bezithembile, besenza ngcono esikolweni, kwaye baphephe ukuziphatha okuyingozi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "False"
msgstr "Bubuxoki"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Actually, teens feel more loved and supported when each caregiver spends time with them in their own way. Caring role models can help teens feel more confident, do better in school, and avoid risky behaviour."
msgstr "Ngokwenene! Abantwana abafikisayo baziva bethandwa kakhulu kwaye bexhaswa xana umnakekeli ngamnye echitha ixesha nabo ngendlela abafuna ngayo. Imizekelo yabantu abanenkathalo inokunceda abantwana abafikisayo bazive bezithembile, besenza ngcono esikolweni, kwaye baphephe ukuziphatha okuyingozi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Not sure"
msgstr "Andiqinisekanga"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Teens feel more loved and supported when each caregiver spends time with them in their own way. Caring role models can help teens feel more confident, do better in school, and avoid risky behaviour."
msgstr "Abantwana abafikisayo baziva bethandwa kakhulu kwaye bexhaswa xana umnakekeli ngamnye echitha ixesha nabo ngendlela abafuna ngayo. Imizekelo yabantu abanenkathalo inokunceda abantwana abafikisayo bazive bezithembile, besenza ngcono esikolweni, kwaye baphephe ukuziphatha okuyingozi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Here are some skills to help guide you in spending one-on-one time with your teen!"
msgstr "Nazi ezinye izakhono ezinokunceda ukukukhokhela ekuchitheni ixesha lomnye nomnye kunye nomntwana wakho ofikisayo!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "DAY"
msgstr "USUKU"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Try to do it every day. \n"
"\n"
"Find 5 minutes (or more!) each day when your teen does not have something else they want to do."
msgstr ""
"Zama ukuyenza iintsuku zonke. \n"
"\n"
"Fumana imizuzu emi 5 (okanye ngaphezulu) suku ngalunye xa umntwana wakho ofikisayo engenayo enye into yokwenza."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Many short moments of connection each day or week help build trust and give you more chances to guide your teen than long, serious conversations."
msgstr "Amaxesha amaninzi amafutshane onxibelelwano ngosuku ngalunye okanye evekini anceda ukwakha kwaye akunike amathuba amaninzi ukukhokela mntwana wakho ofikisayo kune ncoko ezinde, nezinzulu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "PLAY"
msgstr "DLALA"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Let your teen choose.\n"
"\n"
"Tell your teen that you would like to spend some time with them and that they can choose what to do or talk about. They might think this is weird at first, but they will come to enjoy this time with you!"
msgstr ""
"Vumela umntwana wakho ofikisayo akhethe.\n"
"\n"
"Mxelele umntana wakho ofikisayo ukuba ungathanda ukuchitha ixesha kunye naye. Kwaye angakwazi ukukhetha into eninokuyenza okanye emanithethe ngayo. Angacinga ukuba ayiqhelekanga ekuqaleni, kodwa uzakubuya alonwabele eli xesha kunye nawe!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "More tips"
msgstr "Ezinye iingcebiso"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "One-on-one time can also help you understand your teen’s online world better. Get involved by asking “Did you come across anything exciting online today?” or “Can you show me how to do a group call on WhatsApp?”"
msgstr "Ixesha lomnye nomnye linganceda nalo ukuqonda ngcondo ilizwe le i-intanethi lomntwana wakho ofikisayo. Zibandakanye ngokubuza \"Ubukhe wadibana nayo nayiphi na into eyonwabisayo kwi-intanethi namhlanje?\" okanye \"Ungakwazi ukundibonisa ukuba yenziwa njani ifowuni yeqela kuWhatsapp?\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "STAY"
msgstr "HLALA"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Focus on your teen.\n"
"\n"
"Switch off the TV and put phones aside. Look at your teen. Nod or say “I see” to show that you are really paying attention. Accept what they say without judging them."
msgstr ""
"Qwalasela kumntwana wakho ofikisayo.\n"
"\n"
"Cima i-UMABONAKUDE ubeke umnxeba ecaleni. Jonga emntwaneni wakho ofikisayo. Nqwala okanye uthi \"ndiyabona\" ukubonakalisa ukuba unike ingqwalasela. Kwamnkele akuthethayo ngaphandle kokumgxeka."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Spending one-on-one time with your teen can be hard to plan. \n"
"\n"
"**Remember to use your new skills:**\n"
"📅 **DAY**: try to do it every day\n"
"⚽ **PLAY**: let your teen choose how to spend one-on-one time  \n"
"🎯 **STAY**: be focused on your teen"
msgstr ""
"Ukuchitha ixesha lomnye nomnye kunye nomntwana wakho ofikisayo kunganzima ukulicwangcisa. \n"
"\n"
"**Khumbula ukusebenzisa izakhono zakho ezintsha.**\n"
"📅 **USUKU**. zama ukuyenza yonke imihla\n"
"⚽ **DLALA** vumela umntwwana wakho ofikisayo akhethe ukuchitha ixesha lomnye nomnye  \n"
"🎯 **HLALA** yibanengqwalasela kumntwana wakho ofikisayo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What could you do to spend one-on-one time with your teen?"
msgstr "Yintoni ongayenza ukuchitha ixesha lomnye nomnye kunye nomntwana wakho ofikisayo?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Do a TikTok dance challenge"
msgstr "Enza umceli-mngeni womdaniso kaTikTok"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Play a game/sport"
msgstr "Dlalani umdlalo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Watch something online"
msgstr "Ubukela into kwi-intanethi"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Prepare dinner"
msgstr "Lungisani isidlo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Eat breakfast/lunch/dinner"
msgstr "Yityani isidlo sakusasa/esasemini/idinala"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Great idea! \n"
"\n"
"Feel like you have NO TIME and you are exhausted? Remember to also think of ways that do not take up extra time, like doing a chore together while chatting."
msgstr ""
"Ngumbono Omhle! \n"
"\n"
"Uziva ingathi AWUNAXESHA kwaye udiniwe? Khumbula ngendlela ezingenakuthatha ixesha lakho elongezelelweyo, njengokwenza umsebenzi wasekaya kunye ngelixa nincokola."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "This week's home activity is to spend 5-15 minutes of one-on-one time with your teen, every day that you can."
msgstr "Kuleveki umsebenzi wasekhaya kukuchitha imizuzu 5-15 yexesha lomnye nomnye kunye nomntwana wakho ofikisayo, ngosuku ngalunye ukuba ninako."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can you spend one-on-one time with your teen this week?"
msgstr "Ungakwazi ukuchitha ixesha lomnye nomnye kunye nomntwana wakho ofikisayo kule veki?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "Ewe"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's great! Caregivers who spend focused one-on-one time with their teens can build trust and love!"
msgstr "Kuhle! Abanakekeli abachitha ingqwalasela kwixesha lomnye nomnye kunye nabantwana babo abafikisayo bangakwazi ukwakha ukuthembana kunye no thando!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I think so"
msgstr "Ndicinga njalo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "You can do it! Try spending just a few minutes each day with your teen. Remember that you can always think of ways that do not take up extra time, like walking to the shop or preparing dinner together."
msgstr "Ungayenza! Zama ukuchitha imizuzu embalwa kunye nomntwana wakho ofikisayo usuku ngalunye. Khumbula ukuba ungakwazi ukucinga ngeendlela ezingenakuthatha xesha elongezelelweyo, njengokuhamba ngenyawo ukuya evenkileni okanye ukulungiselela isidlo sangokuhlwa kunye."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "No"
msgstr "Hayi"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's okay. Spending focused time with your teen will become easier as you build a routine. At first, you can try to think of ways that do not take up extra time, like doing a chore together."
msgstr "Kulungile. Ukuchitha ixesha nomntwana wakho ofikisayo kuzakubalula njengokuba nisakha inkqubo. Ekuqaleni, ungazama ukucinga ngeendlela ezingazokuthatha ixesha elongezelelweyo, njengokwenza imisebenzi yasekhaya kunye."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Remember, spending even a few minutes of one-on-one time with your teen each day can strengthen your relationship and build trust. \n"
"\n"
"Listening closely and sharing small moments helps teens feel loved and supported."
msgstr ""
"Khumbula, ukuchitha imizuzwana yexesha lomnye nomnye nomntwana wakho ofikisayo ngosuku ngalunye bungabuqinisa ubudlelwane benu kwaye nakhe ukuthembana. \n"
"\n"
"Ukumamelela kufutshane kunye nokwabelana ngemizuzu emancinci kunganceda umntwana wakho ofikisayo azive ethandwa kwaye exhasekile."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_daughter_1.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Here's what @data.characters.media_daughter_1.name has to say about one-on-one time with her mother"
msgstr "Nantsi enye @data.characters.media_daughter_1.name angakuyithetha malunga nexesha lomnye nomnye kunye nomama wakhe"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"When my mother asked to spend time with me, I thought “Maybe something is wrong, maybe she is sick.” But she said “No, I just want to spend time.” I was sceptical, but I accepted.\n"
"\n"
"She asked me what I like doing. It was strange and I was not comfortable, because she never ever spent time with me on my own.\n"
"\n"
"The more she kept on trying and we spent this time together, it felt really nice. She got to share her own childhood with me, things I never heard before. That helped me to also share what is going on in my life. We even talk about boyfriends and about problems I have. I know I can talk to my mother now."
msgstr ""
"Xa umama wam ecela ukuba achithe ixesha kunye nam, Bendicinga \"Mhlawumbi ikhona into engalunganga, mhlawubi uyagula\". Kodwa wathi \"Hayi, ndifuna nje ukuchitha ixesha\". Ndandithandabuza, kodwa ndayamnkela.\n"
"\n"
"Wandibuza ukuba ndithanda ukwenza ntoni na. Yayingaqhelekanga kwaye ndandingakhululekanga, kuba akazange achithe ixesha kunye nam ndindodwa.\n"
"\n"
" Qho emana ezama kwaye sichithe elixesha kunye, bekuvakala kamnandi. Uye wandibalisela ngokukhula kwakhe, izinto endangazange ndizive ngaphambili. Lonto indincede ukuba nam ndibalise ngokuqhubekekayo ebomini bam. Siye sathetha nangamakhwenkwe kwakunye nezinye iingxaki endinazo. Ndiyayazi ukuba ndingakwazi ukuthethe nomama wam ngoku."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Well done for taking time for yourself today. 🎉"
msgstr "Wenze kakuhle ngokuthatha ixesha lesiqu sakho namhlanje. 🎉"

